    footer(
      role="footer"
      ) 

      h2 Delivery of premade packages for your visitors

      .footer-text_container
        .footer-text
          h3 Party = worries? Not with us!
          p How much food should I prepare? Which wine should I choose? Will they like this cheese? Stop worrying. In our packages you will find everything you need for your visitors: quality food from farmers, good drinks that goes well with the meals and even all the necessary accessories including details like serviettes, trays, candles etc.
        .footer-text
          h3 You can be sure your visitors will be pleased
          p Do you want to impress your visitors and make your name as a great host? With us you can be certain to do that. We pay the maximum attention to the selection of meals. All the ingredients are from czech farmers, wines are from moravian wineyards. Everything is fresh and quality-tested. Our packages just work and your guests will be pleased.
        .footer-text
          h3 Don't spend time shopping. ENJOY YOURSELF!
          p Shopping is boring and can be demanding if you want quality. Visit farmer's markets, speciality shops - where should you find the time? Don't despair, we will do this for you. You just choose your package and wait in the comfort of your home for the delivery that contains everything that you need for your party or a surprise visit.